node.text:
Kicked off the amateur circuit for being too violent, Russian welterweight Vasilii Anthokii got a call from @karatecombat
 president @adam_skovacs asking if he wanted to turn pro.
 
Thursday night, 10pm on CBS Sports (ET) and Eurosport (CET), watch him take on French veteran @DavyDona_hurricane. 
 
If @_mr.va_ wins here, he’s putting the whole welterweight division on notice!

Watch tonight on CBS Sports Network // free replays on Sunday at the Karate Combat YouTube channel.

node.text:
Punching underwater set with my @hydrorevolution_fitness. I take a deep breath in through my nose then jump in the pool. When I reach the bottom of the pool, I release half of the air in my lungs to avoid floating back to the surface. Always go for short reps, intensity & power instead of length & volume for this exercise. 

Click the link in my bio and use code “TRAINWITHGSP” to check out the equipment and get 20% off!

node.text:
Glute leg raises on my BaseBench Pro by @baseblocks!

Make sure you keep your hips perpendicular to the floor and point your toes. Switch it up by changing the elastic settings between sets. Remember to keep the maximum muscular contraction during the peak of your movement!

Link in my bio to check out the equipment.

node.text:
La chaleur et l’humidité d’aujourd’hui ont fait de mon training un enfer 😩. Malgré tout, j’essaie toujours de repousser mes limites. Moi vs moi! 💪🏻

Heat and humidity made today’s training extremely painful… But I always try to push my limits no matter what. Me vs me! 💪🏻

No excuse!!
